    <item>
      <title>英国央行明年将削减 1000 亿英镑债券投资组合</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/boe-to-reduce-bond-portfolio-by-100-billion-over-next-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行将继续保持减少债券资产负债表的速度，这一决定可能会影响财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯在即将到来的预算中拥有多少财政火力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/boe-to-reduce-bond-portfolio-by-100-billion-over-next-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 11:09:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰因通胀加剧延长利率暂停期限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/ukraine-extends-interest-rate-pause-as-inflation-flares-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰央行连续第二次会议维持利率不变，表明尽管战时预算压力越来越大，政策制定者不会容忍通胀上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/ukraine-extends-interest-rate-pause-as-inflation-flares-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 11:00:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国央行誓言采取渐进式宽松政策，利率以 8:1 票数维持不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/boe-vows-gradual-approach-to-easing-as-rates-held-in-8-1-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行警告投资者，其不会急于放松政策，暂缓再次下调借贷成本，并做出另一项决定，维持资产负债表缩减的步伐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/boe-vows-gradual-approach-to-easing-as-rates-held-in-8-1-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 11:00:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
